      "content": "it’s not temporary though. there’s no \"authentic person\" left to find. the version of me that actually mattered, the one people actually respected... that version is gone. it’s like I’m just haunted by someone who doesn't exist anymore. it feels more like a permanent end than just a bad phase.",
